moji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n時間值同縮IV</blockquote><br />\n巴打係入面做緊？<br />\n我有諗呢樣 急升就話姐 但有時真係正股郁都唔郁 5分鐘即冇20格 何來有iv 同時間值可言<br />\n真心求教</blockquote><br />\n知呢隻野既缺點 唔洗入面就都答到你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n先求知 ，再投資啦"},{"pid":"aa395a03d081344970047f71c2e30535256a13e1","tid":423893,"uid":35930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T12:50:20.000Z","msg":"就係唔郁 所以先縮窩"},{"pid":"f72640dc890facddfc6b73fd0e5f95d5d8778651","tid":423893,"uid":48762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T15:15:32.000Z","msg":"留名學野"},{"pid":"3889c2313d22d747bddb14cf670ac99ac2d95ce1","tid":423893,"uid":123587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T16:04:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想請教其實縮窩係用咩機制 <br />\n點解成日正股無變  無啦啦畀人縮20格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n時間值同縮IV</blockquote><br />\n巴打係入面做緊？<br />\n我有諗呢樣 急升就話姐 但有時真係正股郁都唔郁 5分鐘即冇20格 何來有iv 同時間值可言<br />\n真心求教</blockquote><br />\n窩=引伸波幅，即係市場預計股價波動性。股價急升/跌，引伸波幅上升，窩輪價格上升。相反股價平穩升/跌，引伸波幅下降，窩輪價格下降。"},{"pid":"b102e0d58bb9a6b0ba99e2fdb4e4682cfae5a825","tid":423893,"uid":123587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T16:10:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想請教其實縮窩係用咩機制 <br />\n點解成日正股無變  無啦啦畀人縮20格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n時間值同縮IV</blockquote><br />\n巴打係入面做緊？<br />\n我有諗呢樣 急升就話姐 但有時真係正股郁都唔郁 5分鐘即冇20格 何來有iv 同時間值可言<br />\n真心求教</blockquote><br />\n窩=引伸波幅，即係市場預計股價波動性。股價急升/跌，引伸波幅上升，窩輪價格上升。相反股價平穩升/跌，引伸波幅下降，窩輪價格下降。</blockquote><br />\n牛熊無引伸波幅，不過直接<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n重有一陣一定有傻仔沖出黎話股票期權公平，我肯定佢玩極都係D QQ/5仔/平保期權。基本上引伸波幅係莊家開出，所有莊家都係PK，你識玩識計價玩窩輪/期權都一樣，除非你做期權short(即做莊家)"},{"pid":"6a2e097fb673258dcd353a44a812365bfeca9c1d","tid":423893,"uid":37389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T16:19:30.000Z","msg":"曾經做過輪枱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔計輪商玩野或者錯價，delta以外都仲有好多因素嘅，買本futures, options and other derivatives 睇下啦，無數底都起碼上cs, jpm或者傻珍個網睇下簡介 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8cac4f20cbdaeff8410e14cc8a78b5a8cfdcdfe","tid":423893,"uid":37389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T16:24:13.000Z","msg":"如果縮vol，都係睇啲hedging instruments 嘅vol有無變，有無liquidity，個市點position ，demand supply，之類啦，輪商其實係最悶嘅market marker，都係賺spread，唔通坐死哂同你賭咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5af6b47f49cc5ffe6a6856fdb6d4a5ac6cb3b5d3","tid":423893,"uid":44229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T16:42:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想請教其實縮窩係用咩機制 <br />\n點解成日正股無變  無啦啦畀人縮20格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n時間值同縮IV</blockquote><br />\n巴打係入面做緊？<br />\n我有諗呢樣 急升就話姐 但有時真係正股郁都唔郁 5分鐘即冇20格 何來有iv 同時間值可言<br />\n真心求教</blockquote><br />\n窩=引伸波幅，即係市場預計股價波動性。股價急升/跌，引伸波幅上升，窩輪價格上升。相反股價平穩升/跌，引伸波幅下降，窩輪價格下降。</blockquote><br />\n牛熊無引伸波幅，不過直接<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n重有一陣一定有傻仔沖出黎話股票期權公平，我肯定佢玩極都係D QQ/5仔/平保期權。基本上引伸波幅係莊家開出，所有莊家都係PK，你識玩識計價玩窩輪/期權都一樣，除非你做期權short(即做莊家)</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n理論上係咁, 股價急升/跌, 之後平穩番縮價既話好合理。但就係會有情況輪商玩野, 牛熊都照縮你5,6格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。就係想知其實會唔會有輪商既縮窩準則, 抑或真係睇心情。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87403cc15acc5746a7161dd77d6ffba31def93f1","tid":423893,"uid":44229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T16:43:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>曾經做過輪枱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔計輪商玩野或者錯價，delta以外都仲有好多因素嘅，買本futures, options and other derivatives 睇下啦，無數底都起碼上cs, jpm或者傻珍個網睇下簡介 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打做過邊間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實輪商幾時大機會玩野"},{"pid":"08d543d88570bf94dfefd99221bd0f3bffe49464","tid":423893,"uid":40684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T16:57:40.000Z","msg":"留名睇俾撚商撚到輸死"},{"pid":"61a7d665031a7d8d9faec09fe7cad384e8fd635b","tid":423893,"uid":89220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T17:23:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想請教其實縮窩係用咩機制 <br />\n點解成日正股無變  無啦啦畀人縮20格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n時間值同縮IV</blockquote><br />\n巴打係入面做緊？<br />\n我有諗呢樣 急升就話姐 但有時真係正股郁都唔郁 5分鐘即冇20格 何來有iv 同時間值可言<br />\n真心求教</blockquote><br />\n窩=引伸波幅，即係市場預計股價波動性。股價急升/跌，引伸波幅上升，窩輪價格上升。相反股價平穩升/跌，引伸波幅下降，窩輪價格下降。</blockquote><br />\n牛熊無引伸波幅，不過直接<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n重有一陣一定有傻仔沖出黎話股票期權公平，我肯定佢玩極都係D QQ/5仔/平保期權。基本上引伸波幅係莊家開出，所有莊家都係PK，你識玩識計價玩窩輪/期權都一樣，除非你做期權short(即做莊家)</blockquote><br />\n牛熊都會出事，個價可以任佢開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正股係咁升，隻牛唔郁，溢價由+2%變負數都仲得，明明街貨量好少"},{"pid":"72ce1c9b6fa23bc0bf6748aa1f571dc1dd141956","tid":423893,"uid":4465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T17:39:22.000Z","msg":"買左邊個輪商？ 邊隻正股既輪？"},{"pid":"68625a5745e3d2b56adfed1d0ca082f6ccec39b4","tid":423893,"uid":4465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T17:40:52.000Z","msg":"一買無廿格係咪買左麥字頭？"},{"pid":"e92fb6926f461aa59803f948be92bc67b1575780","tid":423893,"uid":44229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T17:48:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一買無廿格係咪買左麥字頭？</blockquote><br />\n間間都試過咁縮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n廿格果次最甘係cs  其他5-10格<br />\n<br />\n其實day trade 左幾個月 個個月都正數既<br />\n但就係呢一個點搞唔通 就係想問有冇巴打係issuer 度做緊 分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"181c43042529e27115a0823a4449af18a5a8e93a","tid":423893,"uid":44071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T18:13:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想請教其實縮窩係用咩機制 <br />\n點解成日正股無變  無啦啦畀人縮20格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/